From the moment I started my treatment with Dr. Anashwar and his team at Denté, I knew I was in good hands. The clinic is not only top-notch and equipped with the latest in dental technology, but it also has a welcoming atmosphere that made me feel comfortable right from the start. 

Dr. Anashwar has a way of making complex procedures seem simple. He took the time to explain each step of my treatment plan, ensuring I understood and was comfortable with what was coming next. His approach is very personalized, and he always considered my concerns and preferences.

The staff at the clinic are a reflection of Dr. Anashwar’s commitment to excellent patient care. They are kind, attentive, and always went the extra mile to accommodate my schedule and address any anxieties I had about the treatment.

Seeing the results now, I couldn’t be happier. My smile has transformed, and so has my confidence. Choosing Dr. Anashwar was one of the best decisions I’ve made for my dental health.

I wholeheartedly recommend Dr. Anashwar to anyone looking to improve their smile. His expertise, combined with his genuine care for his patients, truly sets him apart!
A very meticulous Doctor. Very skilled. Superb with his hands. Gentle & a perfectionist. Possesses excellent diagnostic & surgical skills. Very happy to be under his treatment
Most pleasant and gentle doctor !! Very  professional *** ************** .   Clinic was clean with proper attention to hygiene !! Doctor had all latest equipment .

Doctor Bhalla  has a very gentle hand and makes his patients very comfortable during the procedures and makes sure to explain everything in detail so that they are prepared....
He also avoids giving unnecessary medications ....His clinic is very neat and welcoming....

It was very pleasant to go through the entire treatment of multiple issues I was facing for last several months. 

I had been to couple of dentists near my residence but none could resolve my problem satisfacorily. I am happy that I came to Dr. Anashwar Bhalla.

Thanks to that visit some other issues of cavity, decay under old crown were discovered and treated in time. He is very thorough, pays attention to detail and is not in a hurry to finish.
I would definetly recommend him to my family and friends. The entire staff is gentle and cultured, hardly any waiting time as it is managed well. Also safe during covid, very spacious clinic, well ventilated. Parking is easy to find.
Finally, with all the treatment done, I am able to eat normally from both sides after a long long time!
